==English==

===Noun===
'''Taxonomic system'''
#{{taxonomy}} a coherent system of [[taxonomic]] judgements on [[circumscription]] and [[placement]] of the considered [[taxon|taxa]]. A taxonomic system will be restricted to a large but limited part of the living world.

::''Current systems for the taxonomy of flowering plants include those by Takhtajan, Cronquist, Thorne and APG. This last has published APG II in 2003 which has gained wide support.''